item.title: Fiber Buildings Offer High Bandwidth
item.description:
Do you want to upgrade your internet speed from slow copper or fixed wireless connections to the rapid speeds offered by fiber optic cables? Are you trying to avoid the high cost of installing new fiber optic cables? If so, you should consider moving into a fiber building. Don’t worry; a fiber building isn’t constructed from exotic materials like carbon fiber. The term “fiber” refers to the type of telecommunication services already available within the building...
